Our Mission

PillPurpose aims to create a comprehensive and user-friendlv website that serves as a platform for community members to access necessary medicines for free, facilitated by generous donations. Recognizing the challenges many individuals face in affording essential medications, the website will act as a bridge between those in need and individuals or organizations willing to donate medications. Through a well-designed and intuitive interface, community members can easily browse through a wide range of available medicines and submit their requests based on their specific requirements. The website will also incorporate a secure and confidential registration system to verify the eligibility of donor institutes with only allowing medical institutions to donate. To facilitate the donation process, the platform will allow donors to list the medications they are willing to contribute and enable easy communication with recipients. A dedicated team of volunteers will be responsible for maintaining the website and ensuring the accuracy of information. Through this project, we aim to foster a sense of community support, making essential medications accessible to those who would otherwise struggle to afford them, ultimately promoting better health outcomes and improving the wellbeing of individuals and families in need.
